title: Reptile-ownership : household penetration rates 2007 to 2013
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Penetration rates, containing a total of 7 data points.
Overall Penetration rates has increased over the Year.
Penetration rates is roughly constant from 2007 to 2008, slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2009, roughly constant from 2009 to 2012, and finally slightly increasing from 2012 to 2013.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
The highest Penetration rates, of value 2.7 was reached at Year 2013
Minimum Penetration rates about 1.5 was reached at Year 2009
